First, generate your private key using the keytool command that comes with the JDK using the following command

    keytool -genkey -v -keystore my-release-key.keystore -alias alias_name -keyalg RSA -keysize 2048 -validity 10000

For more information visit [Generating a private key][1]

Then create a file build.json like below and put it in your &lt;projectfolder&gt;/buildConfig folder 

    {
     &quot;android&quot;: {
         &quot;release&quot;: {
             &quot;keystore&quot;: &quot;my-release-key.keystore&quot;,
             &quot;alias&quot;: &quot;alias_name&quot;,
             &quot;storePassword&quot;: &quot;secretPassword&quot;,
             &quot;password&quot; : &quot;secretPassword&quot;
         }
     }
 }

Keep your my-release-key.keystore file in &lt;projectfolder&gt;/buildConfig folder

Then execute the following command

    ionic cordova build android --prod --release --buildConfig ./buildConfig/build.json

Please upvote the answer if this answer resolved your issue.


  [1]: http://docs.phonegap.com/phonegap-build/signing/android/

