What we&#39;ll do is to simply draw the video on the canvas, and then apply a CSS `filter:blur()` on the canvas element directly from CSS.  
Since we don&#39;t need to account for the spread, the calculations for drawImage are easier, but since we don&#39;t apply any filter, we can even use the lazy version that was in the comments of the second snippet:

